title: 4 Rare 80s Albums [Part 28] Canadian New Wave Bands
description:
The Great White North produced some of the best new wave/synthpop music of the 80s which unfortunately remained obscured even south of the border.  Here are four rare records from four great Canadian bands.


Boys Brigade - Boys Brigade [1983]

Platinum Blonde - Alien Shores [1985]

Spoons - Arias & Symphonies [1982]

The Parachute Club - At The Feet Of The Moon [1984]
